{"title":"fitness","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"deep-sea-fish-oil-capsules-omega-3-2500-mg-lemon","title":"Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules - 2500 mg Omega 3 (Lemon Flavored)","description":"\u003ch2\u003eNeuherbs Deep Sea Fish Oil – Omega-3 Capsules for Daily Wellness\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eLooking for the best fish oil capsules in India? neuherbs \u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003edeep sea fish oil\u003c\/span\u003e offers a triple-strength formula designed to support your overall health. These omega-3 fish oil capsules are lemon-flavoured to eliminate fishy burps, making them the perfect fish oil supplement for men and women alike.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eWhy Choose Neuherbs Fish Oil Capsules?\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eNeuherbs brings you premium-quality fish oil capsules sourced from small deep-sea fish like sardines and anchovies. Rich in EPA and DHA, these omega-3 fish oil capsules deliver 2500 mg of pure fish oil per serving and are added with Vitamins E and D3.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHeart Health:\u003c\/strong\u003e Promotes healthy cholesterol level and supports cardiac function.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBrain Function:\u003c\/strong\u003e Improves memory, focus, \u0026amp; helps manage stress.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSkin \u0026amp; Hair:\u003c\/strong\u003e Among the best fish oil capsules for hair growth and glowing skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eWeight Management:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ideal fish oil capsules for weight loss and metabolism support.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eJoint \u0026amp; Bone Strength:\u003c\/strong\u003e Helps reduce inflammation and aids in muscle recovery.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eProduct Features\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTriple-Strength Omega-3 Fish Oil Capsuless (2500 mg per serving, 2 capsules)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e1486 mg of Omega-3s: 892 mg EPA + 594 mg DHA\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLemon-flavoured softgels – no fishy burps and aftertaste\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFortified with Vitamin D3 and E\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAvailable size includes fish oil 60 capsules and fish oil 200 capsules\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for all: \u003cstrong\u003efish oil capsules for women\u003c\/strong\u003e improve hormone health and promote healthy pregnancy and fish oil capsules for men aid in post-workout muscle recovery, and brain and vision health.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eBest-Rated Fish Oil Supplements with Quality You Can Trust\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eOur original fish oil capsules undergo 10 quality checks, including molecular distillation and third-party testing to remove heavy metals like mercury, lead, and arsenic. Whether you're buying your first pack or switching to a cleaner brand, this is the best omega-3 fish oil capsule, acclaimed for purity, potency, and effectiveness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eAffordable Fish Oil Capsules Price in India\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eWith neuherbs, you don’t just get the best omega-3 capsules, you get premium quality at a great value. Whether you are comparing fish oil capsules price or omega-3 capsules price, our range delivers unmatched benefits for the price.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eWho Should Use This?\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAnyone looking for omega-3 fish oil capsules for daily heart and brain health\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePeople seeking fish oil capsules for skin ageing or fish oil capsules for hair growth\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFitness enthusiasts using fish oil capsules for weight loss and recovery\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMen and women looking to fill their omega-3 nutritional gap naturally\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Fish Oil - (60 Softgel)","offer_id":40975800926378,"sku":"NDSFO60","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Fish Oil - (120 Softgel)","offer_id":46561937785002,"sku":"NDSFO120","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Fish Oil - (200 Softgel)=Recommended","offer_id":44663434936490,"sku":"NDSFO200","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/deep_sea_fish_oil_1.png?v=1756897940"},{"product_id":"true-vitamin-tablets-antioxidants-blend-wellness","title":"Neuherbs True Vitamin Daily Tablets","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eDoes the diet you are taking are full of vitamins, minerals, healthy fats \u0026amp;amp; antioxidants? And if yes, does it get properly absorbed by your body? Do you still feel lethargic after eating healthy food? The answer to all these questions is fulfilment of daily nutritional\u0026amp;nbsp;needs with appropriate absorption. And it is not an easy task. But including a multivitamin into the daily diet can help. Neuherbs True Vitamin Daily multivitamin tablet is formulated with 22 key ingredients which are validated by science to provide various\u0026amp;nbsp;health benefits. Neuherbs Multivitamin is a solution for today’s unhealthy habits of binging on fast food that only offers empty calories \u0026amp;amp; zero nutrition. We designed this formula of Multivitamin (Vitamin A, E, C, D \u0026amp;amp; B complex) Multimineral (Zinc, Magnesium, Copper, Selenium,) along with ginseng and antioxidant from Grape Seed extract (95% Proanthocyanins) to help you provide overall strength, stamina, enhanced immunity, support heart, brain health and improve quality of life.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":40975804891306,"sku":"NMV60","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Value Pack - (120 Tablets)=Recommended","offer_id":40975804858538,"sku":"NMV120","price":798.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/best_multivitamin_for_men.webp?v=1770728293"},{"product_id":"ashwagandha-1000-plus-tablets-stress-relief","title":"Ashwagandha 1000 Plus Tablets – Daily Lifestyle Support","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Ashwagandha 1000 Plus is made with natural ashwagandha root extract, Vitamin E, and B-complex (B6, B9, B12), along with piperine. This blend is designed to \u003cstrong data-start=\"1412\" data-end=\"1497\"\u003ehelp maintain balance, support an active lifestyle, and promote everyday wellness\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":40975944614058,"sku":"NA1000P60","price":319.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Months Pack - (120 Tablets)=Recommended","offer_id":41395707478186,"sku":"NA1000P60P2-1","price":598.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/ashwagandha_tablets_1000_plus_1.jpg?v=1754394534"},{"product_id":"pure-himalayan-shilajit-resin-boost-stamina","title":"Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin - Boost Stamina \u0026 Strength","description":"\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\" class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShilajit is a traditional Ayurvedic herb that has been used for centuries to help people with low stamina, endurance, and vitality. neuherbs shilajit resin is sourced from the high altitudes of the Himalayas for high potency \u0026amp; better results. neuherbs Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin is purified using a Traditional Ayurvedic technique known as Suryataapi to retain its nutrients, benefits, and effectiveness. So, try neuherbs ’ Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin and improve your strength, stamina \u0026amp; energy while reducing fatigue and getting your testosterone levels significantly higher. Since it is sourced from high ~18000 ft. altitudes, it offers you up to 75% of fulvic acid and the most potent form for optimal absorption and efficacy. neuherbs Pure Himalayan Shilajit is completely safe as it is tested for heavy metals from NABL.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Shilajit - (20 GM)","offer_id":44586359816362,"sku":"NPHS20","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Shilajit - (30 GM)=Recommended","offer_id":44363347951786,"sku":"NPHS30","price":999.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Pure_himalayan_shilajit_resin_1.webp?v=1769506439"},{"product_id":"organic-ashwagandha-powder-energy-stress-relief","title":"Ashwagandha Powder - Boost Energy, Reduce Stress","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eAshwagandha is an evergreen Ayurvedic medicinal herb that’s been used for over 3000 years to promote health and wellbeing. Also referred to as the Indian Ginseng, Ashwagandha helps rejuvenate body and mind alike, manage stress, improve mood, induce calmness, increase stamina and energy levels, manage inflammation, and reduce oxidative stress. Ashwagandha helps manage insomnia, stress, anxiety, and promote calmness in mind \u0026amp; body. Ashwagandha also contains antioxidants that are known to improve immunity. Ashwagandha powders are designed to improve sleep quality and sleep cycle, relax the mind, and manage tiredness and general fatigue that’s associated with all day stress. neuherbs 100% pure \u0026amp; natural Ashwagandha Powder is made from the finest Ashwagandha root to access the maximum benefits of withanolides:the active ingredient of ashwagandha. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1  - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426208776362,"sku":"NOASP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2 - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801787293866,"sku":"NOASP100P2","price":398.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Ashwagandha_powder_1_668accd6-0b57-4208-9f34-d349d5e07884.png?v=1766468142"},{"product_id":"organic-shatavari-powder-womens-health","title":"Organic Shatavari Powder For Women's Hormonal Balance","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eShatavari root is an Ayurvedic medicinal herb used extensively in Ayurveda to promote women’s reproductive health and wellness. neuherbs  organic Shatavari Powder is a crucial herbal tonic that helps improve women's hormones and strength by nourishing, strengthening, and maintaining the female reproductive health. neuherbs  Shatavari powder is prepared using organic Shatavari roots in a quality-controlled and certified facility. Our highly efficient Shatavari Powder offers various health benefits—it helps improve digestion, regulate the female reproductive system, reduce body fatigue and boost physical strength. It may also help you manage hormonal imbalance. As an ayurvedic herb, Shatavari also helps our body to cope with stress, anxiety, and mood swings.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1 - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426126725290,"sku":"NOSTP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2 - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801897099434,"sku":"NOSTP100P2","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Shatavari_powder_1.webp?v=1762412855"},{"product_id":"true-calcium-plant-based-vitamin-d3","title":"True Calcium Tablets with Plant Vitamin D3 for Stronger Bones","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAn amazing 3-in-1 supplement for daily bone and muscle care, neuherbs True Calcium supplement by neuherbs contains 1000 mg of calcium in a more bioavailable Calcium Citrate form, more-bioavailable Vitamin D3, and natural Magnesium. All three vital nutrients work together to maintain strong bones, increase bone density, support muscle, tendon relaxation and contraction, reducing the risk of fractures and brittle bones later in life. True Calcium, the plant-based calcium tablets, help fill the daily calcium gap in adults. Paired with Vitamin D3 it supports better absorption of calcium in the body. Th unique combination of magnesium \u0026amp; calcium in these calcium tablets for bones works synergistically to support muscles contraction, relaxation \u0026amp; improve overall flexibility.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":44271815033002,"sku":"NTC60","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":46152267366570,"sku":"NTC60P2","price":598.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/true_calcium_tablets_1.png?v=1747133307"},{"product_id":"mini-deep-sea-fish-oil-1000-mg","title":"Mini Deep Sea Fish Oil 1000 mg (Lemon Flavour)","description":"\u003cp\u003eAre you looking for fish oil small capsules that are easy to swallow? neuherbs’ Mini Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules solves your problem. Introducing the most potent source of Omega-3 fatty acids in a remarkably compact form. While regular \u003cstrong\u003efish oil capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e can be large and difficult to swallow, these omega 3 mini capsules offer a convenient and effective alternative.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThese small size \u003cstrong\u003eomega 3 capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e are 50% smaller than regular fish oil capsules, yet they deliver double the strength, providing 360mg of EPA and 240mg of DHA per softgel. Each mini fish oil pill also contains Vitamin E (100% RDA) and Vitamin D3 (100% RDA) to improve bone and skin health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition, forget about the unpleasant fishy taste – these mini fish oil capsules are infused with a refreshing lemon flavour to eliminate fishy aftertaste and burps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eMini Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules Benefits\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs the only brand offering smallest fish oil capsules in India in natural lemon flavour, neuherbs scientifically researched product delivers a range of health benefits:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImproves Heart Health: Omega-3 fatty acids, especially EPA, help maintain healthy cholesterol levels and blood pressure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnhances Brain Function: DHA are crucial for cognitive function, memory, and focus.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces Inflammation: Omega-3s possess anti-inflammatory properties that may help alleviate joint pain and muscle soreness.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eVitamins D and E: Vitamin E improves absorption of Omega-3s, while Vitamin D ensures healthy bones and cartilage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eneuherbs Quality Assurance\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs is committed to delivering the highest quality omega 3 fish oil mini softgels in India. We test the fish for heavy metal toxicity, including mercury, cobalt, copper, and cadmium, through a process called molecular distillation that offers 100% accurate results. In addition, each batch undergoes rigorous ten-step testing for purity, potency, and freshness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eRecommended Dosage and Packaging\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs \u003cstrong\u003eomega 3 fish oil\u003c\/strong\u003e mini softgels are available in packs of 120 capsules. For best results, take one small fish oil pill twice daily with a meal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eConsult an expert for free to learn more about your heart health and the benefits of Omega-3 fish oils. Add neuherbs’ Mini Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules to your everyday routine and experience the numerous benefits of concentrated Omega-3s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Mini Fish Oil - (120 Softgel)","offer_id":44930057732266,"sku":"NMDSFO120","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Mini Fish Oil - (60 Softgel)","offer_id":47466409525418,"sku":"NMDSFO60","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Mini Fish Oil - (200 Softgel)","offer_id":44930057765034,"sku":"NMDSFO200","price":999.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Mini_deep_sea_fish_oil_120.webp?v=1772186300"},{"product_id":"true-multivitamin-tablets-women-health","title":"True Vitamin Women: Multivitamin Tablets For Women","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated explicitly for adult women to help manage their daily nutritional needs. neuherbs True Vitamin Women multivitamin tablets contains 34 ingredients including four essential blends that provide comprehensive wellness support. The multivitamin tablets offer 100% RDA of essential vitamins with vital minerals, amino acids, and plant-based vitamin D3, which help women nourish and improve their bones, heart, immunity, and hair- skin effectively. These multivitamin tablets for women help manage hormonal balance, elevated mood and poor reproductive health. The amino acids with vitamin b complex help with fatigue and boost energy levels required to carry out daily tasks effectively.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","bran