 Ultra Capsules to Boost Men's Performance","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eneuherbs Shilajit Ultra Gold Capsule for men, has 11 powerful Ayurvedic ingredients such as \u0026amp;\u0026amp; Ashwagandha, Shatavari, Cinnamon, Gokshura, Lavang, Jaiphal, kesar, and Swarna Bhasma. Ayurveda says these ingredients are used as Rasayana, to promote longevity, energy levels and stamina. The herbs have antioxidant, anti-inflammatory, rejuvenating properties, helping with endurance, stamina, performance and motivation. Shilajit gold ultra capsules also help in enhancing mood, sleep and reduce stress offering a positive effect on overall testosterone levels. The addition of kali mirch extract also known as piperine ensures that the body absorbs the nutrients present in neuherbs Shilajit Ultra Gold Capsules effectively, making our shilajit capsules one of the most effective in increasing your performance \u0026amp; stamina!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - 60 Capsules","offer_id":44919565713578,"sku":"NSGU60","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Value Pack - 120 Capsules","offer_id":46122557571242,"sku":"NSGU60P2","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Shilajit_gold_ultra_capsules_1.png?v=1751715137"},{"product_id":"true-magnesium-tablets-relax-muscles-mind","title":"True Magnesium Tablets - Relax Muscles \u0026 Mind, Support Bones","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMagnesium is essential for proper heart function, energy production, hormonal balance, and muscle function. It is essentially known as the “Miracle Mineral” because of its versatile benefits. It also helps our body absorb Vitamin D3 better, promotes healthy nervous function, improves bone health, calms the mind, regulates insulin production, and keeps the body energized throughout the day. neuherbs True Magnesium is a high strength formula that contains 1600 mg of magnesium, that is uniquely paired with Zinc, Vitamin C, antioxidants like Blueberry, and Bilberry for maximum benefits. True Magnesium is created to fulfil your body’s daily magnesium needs. True Magnesium supplement contains 353mg of elemental Magnesium Bisglycinate in a more bioavailable form which is gentle on stomach. It effectively contributes to keeping the muscle relaxed, helps improve energy levels, promote sound sleep, calms the mind, fights free-radical damage, improves immunity \u0026amp; promote better muscle recovery.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Value Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":48022649733290,"sku":"NTMG120","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Smart Pack - 60 Tablets","offer_id":44923837153450,"sku":"NTMG60","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/True_magnesium_tablets_9.webp?v=1771494334"},{"product_id":"b12-vitamin-tablets-energy-circulation","title":"Plant-Based True Vitamin B12 Tablets For Energy \u0026 Brain","description":"\u003cp\u003eVitamin B12 deficiency can lead to tiredness, muscle soreness, muscle cramps, uninvited fatigue, depression, and even mood swings. Vitamin B12 supplements are best for vegans \u0026amp; vegetarians that may promote better circulation, improve concentration and memory, keep the mind calm, promote nerve health, reduce tiredness, improve energy levels, and boost metabolic processes. It's the best Vitamin B12 supplement which consists of natural Vitamin B12 derived from spirulina to help you fulfill your daily Vitamin B12 needs. True B12 Vitamin tablet for men and women with Myo-Inositol which help promote better absorption that help maintain optimal brain functioning, reduce stress \u0026amp; anxiety and is a good mood enhancer. In addition, neuherbs True B12 Vitamin also contains folic acid and the goodness of Punarnava. Punarnava is best known for its rejuvenating properties that help the body recover oxidative stress and rejuvenate the body from within.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":44928074416298,"sku":"NTB1260","price":275.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":46152288469162,"sku":"NTB1260P2","price":549.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/true_b12_tablets_1.png?v=1744629336"},{"product_id":"pure-himalayan-shilajit-gummies-stamina","title":"Pure Himalayan Shilajit Gummies 30 (Tamarind Flavour) for Stamina","description":"\u003cp\u003eShilajit is a traditional Ayurvedic herb that has been used for centuries to treat people with low stamina, endurance, and vitality. neuherbs Pure Himalayan Shilajit Gummies are not only powerfully packed with original Himalayan shilajit resin, sourced from the high altitudes of the Himalayas, but are also available in a delicious and effortless gummy format. This new Shilajit resin gummy is recognized as the best gummies for strength, stamina and vitality, and uniquely delivers the benefits of Shilajit; with the added deliciousness of tamarind flavour! Offering all the advantages of pure shilajit resin, neuherbs Shilajit gummies provide a convenient option that can be consumed without water, offering flexibility and ease of consumption. Whether you need an energy boost before a workout or desire a sweet indulgence after a meal, simply chew these gummies anytime, anywhere, for an effortless wellness experience. The shilajit gummies are free from added sugar, artificial preservatives \u0026amp; gelatin free.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack- 30N Gummies","offer_id":45124596891818,"sku":"NPHSG30TMF","price":499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Value Pack - 60N Gummies","offer_id":46122560848042,"sku":"NPHSG30TMFP2","price":998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/buybestpureshilajitgummiesonline.jpg?v=1700545662"},{"product_id":"deep-sea-cod-liver-oil-capsules-for-heart-brain","title":"Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules for Heart \u0026 Brain","description":"\u003cp\u003eAre you looking for a natural alternative to fish oil supplements to boost your heart and brain health? \u003cstrong\u003eCod liver oil capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e are an excellent choice. neuherbs Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules 600 mg offer a potent blend of Omega-3 fatty acids (180mg), Vitamin D3, and Vitamin E in one convenient soft gel. Obtained from the depths of the Atlantic and Pacific oceans, our cod liver oil is a rich source of essential nutrients that support overall well-being.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCod fish is a time-tested source of Omega-3s, known for their numerous health benefits. These fish get their Omega-3s by absorbing the microalgae after consuming phytoplanktons. Each capsule contains high levels of EPA and DHA, vital for maintaining a healthy heart and sharp mind. Cod liver oil also contains vitamins A and D and remarkable anti-inflammatory properties. So, with neuherbs, you not only get the benefits of Omega-3 fatty acids, but also 100% RDA of Vitamin A, D, and E.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhat’s more? Our lemon-flavoured capsules eliminate the unpleasant aftertaste and fishy burps commonly associated with cod liver oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eCod Liver Oil Capsules Benefits\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules offer a range of health benefits:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKeeps Your Heart Healthy: Omega-3 fatty acids help maintain healthy cholesterol levels and blood pressure, promoting cardiovascular wellness.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImproves Your Brain Function: DHA is crucial for cognitive function, memory, and focus, supporting a sharp and healthy mind.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBoosts Your Immunity: Vitamin D3 and anti-inflammatory drugs help modulate the immune system and keep infections at bay.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaintains Healthy Bones: Vitamin D3 is essential for calcium absorption and bone health, ensuring you have stronger bones, cartilage, and muscles.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffers Antioxidant Support: Vitamin E acts as a powerful antioxidant, protecting cells from oxidative damage. This helps improve gut, skin, and hair health.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNourishes Skin: The anti-inflammatory properties and antioxidants together help boost skin cell production, protect them from stress and inflammation, and reduce the signs of ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eCod Liver Oil Benefits for Female\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOmega-3 fatty acids, particularly DHA, are essential during pregnancy for fetal brain development. It can potentially improve your unborn baby’s brain function and retina development. By taking the best cod liver oil for adults, you can also reduce the risks of preterm delivery.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eneuherbs Quality Check\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs delivers high-quality health supplements with scientifically tested formulations. Our Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil undergoes molecular distillation and third-party testing for purity, efficiency, and safety. Free from preservatives, artificial colours, flavours, and gluten, they are the best cod liver oil capsules in India.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eDosage and Packaging\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs \u003cstrong\u003eDeep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules Omega 3\u003c\/strong\u003e are available in bottles of 100 capsules. For best results, take one capsule twice daily with a meal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eConsult with a healthcare professional to learn more about your specific health needs and the benefits of Omega-3 fatty acids, Vitamin D3, and Vitamin E.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Deep Sea Cod Liver - (100 softgel)","offer_id":46151832600746,"sku":"NDSCLO100","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Deep_sea_cod_liver_oil_1.webp?v=1767179761"},{"product_id":"ashwagandha-500mg-60-tablets","title":"Ashwagandha 500 mg - 60 Tablets: Boosts Energy \u0026 Immunity","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Ashwagandha Tablets offer 500 mg of ashwagandha root extract that contains 3.5% withanolides- the active component of ashwagandha herb. Ashwagandha has been known as a natural energy booster that help improve physical performance and body strength, aiding energy metabolism and reducing fatigue to keep you energized all day long. Due to the antioxidant \u0026amp;amp; anti-inflammatory properties, ashwagandha root extract also acts as an immunity enhancer, protecting body cells from oxidative stress and supporting healthy immune function. Ashwagandha tablets can be easily incorporated in daily life to cope with daily life stress and fatigue, due to its stress-reducing properties contributing to overall improved mental clarity, focus sleep quality, and body revitalization.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack- 